    <h2 id="why-creatine-beginners">Why Creatine Gummies Are the Perfect Starting Point for New Users</h2>

    <p>Creatine monohydrate is the single most effective legal sports supplement ever studied. Over 500 peer-reviewed studies confirm that 3-5g daily increases muscle phosphocreatine stores, enhancing strength, power output, and muscle recovery. The International Society of Sports Nutrition, the American College of Sports Medicine, and the National Strength and Conditioning Association all endorse creatine monohydrate as safe and effective. Yet many beginners never start — deterred by the powder mixing ritual, the gritty texture, the chalky taste, or simple confusion about dosing.</p>

