    </div>

    <p>Creatine gummies solve every practical barrier that prevents beginners from starting. Pre-measured servings eliminate dosing guesswork. The gummy format eliminates mixing, shaking, and dealing with undissolved powder. The taste is genuinely enjoyable rather than chalky. And the portability means you can take creatine anywhere — at the gym, at the office, or while traveling — without a shaker bottle or water source.</p>

