      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <strong>Expected results timeline</strong>
        <p>Week 1-2: Initial weight gain (1-3 lbs) from intracellular water retention. Week 3-4: Full muscle saturation. Week 4-8: Measurable strength and power increases in trained movements.</p>
      </div>
