      <p><strong>Beginner tip:</strong> Do not skip rest days. Creatine works through muscle saturation, not acute dosing. Taking it only on training days will result in lower average muscle creatine levels and reduced effectiveness. Think of it like a daily vitamin — consistency matters more than timing.</p>
